TaskAttributionTiming.summary: NOTE Experimental The TaskAttributionTiming interface returns information about the work involved in a long task and its associate frame context. The frame context, also called the container, is the iframe, embed or object that is being implicated, on the whole, for a long task.

remarks.para: You usually work with TaskAttributionTiming objects when observing long tasks.

TaskAttributionTimingContainerId.summary:
NOTE Experimental The containerId read-only property of the interface returns the container's id
attribute. A container is the iframe, embed or object etc. that is being implicated, on the whole, for a long task.
TaskAttributionTimingContainerId.value: A string containing the container's id HTML content attribute.

TaskAttributionTimingContainerType.summary: NOTE Experimental The containerType read-only property of the interface returns the type of the container, one of iframe, embed, or object.
TaskAttributionTimingContainerType.value: A string containing the container's type, one of iframe, embed, or object. If no type can be determined, window will be returned.

TaskAttributionTimingContainerSrc.summary:
NOTE Experimental The containerSrc read-only property of the interface returns the container's src
attribute. A container is the iframe, embed or object etc. that is being implicated, on the whole, for a long task.
TaskAttributionTimingContainerSrc.value: A string containing the container's src attribute (e.g., <iframe src="url.html">).

TaskAttributionTimingContainerName.summary:
NOTE Experimental The containerName read-only property of the interface returns the container's name
attribute. A container is the iframe, embed or object etc. that is being implicated, on the whole, for a long task.
TaskAttributionTimingContainerName.value: A string containing the container's name HTML content attribute (e.g., <iframe name="myIframe"> or <object name="myObject">).

TaskAttributionTimingToJSON.summary: NOTE Experimental The toJSON() method of the interface is a {{Glossary("Serialization","serializer")}}; it returns a JSON representation of the object.
TaskAttributionTimingToJSON.returns: A {{jsxref("JSON")}} object that is the serialization of the object.
